When Insight Insignia enters, you may attach it to target creature you control.
Whenever equipped creature deals combat damage to a player, surveil 1, then draw a card. (Look at the top card of your library. You may put that card into your graveyard.)
Equip {U}

Equipped creature gets +2/+0.
Whenever equipped creature attacks, return target creature card with lesser power from a graveyard to the battlefield under your control tapped and attacking. Exile it at the beginning of the next end step, or if it would leave the battlefield.
Equip {3}

When Rose Court Claymore enters, you may attach it to target creature you control.
Equipped creature gets +2/+0.
Equip {2}

Equipped creature gets +2/+2 and protection from red and from green.
Whenever equipped creature deals combat damage to a player, exile the top two cards of your library. You may play them until end of turn.  You may play an additional land this turn.
Equip {2}

cards.flavor:
The gods stayed silent as the moments swayed;
as unlikely as it was, peace was had.
The two were able to sit in each other's silence;
remembering the memories of their past.”
—The Koiosode

The call of the Dead was loud and frightful;
beckoning the nyxborn to delve deeper.
For twice memories lost a new one gained;
but were these his or from a fable never told?”
—The Koiosode

“Memories faded as emotions built;
as the Poison-Tongued saw a ripe treat.
Grasping out and holding tight;
memories dissolved overnight”
—The Koiosode
